int main() {
    // Loop to print every 5th number from 10 to 30
    // Start at 10, continue while i <= 30, and increment i by 5 each time
    for (int i = 10; i <= 30; i += 5) {
        printf("%d\n", i);  // Output the current value of i
    }
    return 0;
}
```
**Expected Output:**
```default
10
